---
title: Pea and Lentil Dahl with apple and warm naan
description: Dahl is an inherently comforting dish that's hearty and warming in equal measures. This lightly spiced lentil dahl has the unexpected addition of grated apple which adds subtle taste and texture. Green peas and mild spices make this a vibrant perfect for any occasion.
